# 🛒 Sonik Smart Retail Management System

A modern **Vue 3 + Vite + FastAPI POS Retail System** for managing inventory, billing, suppliers, employees, credit, subscriptions, and Razorpay payments.

---

# ✨ Features

## 🧑‍💼 Store Owner Panel
- 📊 Dashboard (KPIs, revenue analytics)
- 📦 Inventory Management (stock, expiry, damage tracking)
- 💳 POS Billing System (fast checkout)
- 💰 Credit Management
- 🚚 Supplier Management
- 📈 Finance Reports
- 👨‍💼 Employee Management
- 🥛 Milk Subscription System
- 🤖 AI Insights Assistant

---

## 👷 Employee Panel
- 🕒 Shift login/logout tracking
- 📊 Daily sales summary
- ⚠️ Low stock alerts
- 📦 Inventory updates
- 🧾 Billing system access

---

# ⚙️ Prerequisites

Make sure you have installed:

- Node.js >= 16
- npm >= 7
- Python >= 3.8
- Git
- Backend server (FastAPI or Node)

---

# 📦 Project Setup

---

# 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/23f2004126/Software_Engineering_Project
cd Software_Engineering_Project
````

---

# 🖥️ BACKEND SETUP (FastAPI)

## 2️⃣ Create Virtual Environment

```bash
cd backend

python -m venv .venv
```

---

## 3️⃣ Activate Virtual Environment

### Windows

```bash
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Mac / Linux

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
```

---

## 4️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## 5️⃣ Create `.env` file

Create a file named `.env` inside `backend/` and add:

```env
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./data/storefront_v2.db
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@gmail.com
ADMIN_PASSWORD=admin@123
EMPLOYEE_EMAIL=employee@gmail.com
EMPLOYEE_PASSWORD=employee@123
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzpxxxxxxxx
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=xxxxxhLmfn5fCR0UPLv
```

---

## 6️⃣ Run Backend Server

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Backend will run at:

```
http://localhost:8000
```

---

# 🎨 FRONTEND SETUP (Vue 3 + Vite)

## 7️⃣ Move to frontend folder

```bash
cd frontend
```

---

## 8️⃣ Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

---

## 9️⃣ Start frontend server

```bash
npm run dev
```

Frontend will run at:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

# 🚀 RUN COMPLETE PROJECT

After starting both backend and frontend:

| Service  | URL                                            |
| -------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Frontend | [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173) |
| Backend  | [http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000) |

---

# 📌 Tech Stack

## Frontend

* Vue 3
* Vite
* Pinia (State Management)

## Backend

* FastAPI / Node.js
* SQLite / PostgreSQL

## Others

* Razorpay Payment Gateway
* REST APIs

---

# 🧪 Common Issues & Fixes

## ❌ npm not found

Install Node.js → [https://nodejs.org](https://nodejs.org)

---

## ❌ Backend not starting

Make sure virtual environment is activated

---

## ❌ Module not found error

Run:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## ❌ CORS Error

Ensure backend allows:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

